<h5>  Are there any sign-up fees or long-term contracts? </h5>
<p>No, all of our monthly memberships are strictly month-to-month. Cancel any time.</p>
 
<h5>If I purchase Advanced Program Design am I able to use the NLPT gym?</h5>
<p>The program design option does not include an NLPT membership, they must be purchased separately.</p>
 
<h5>I have a friend visiting from out of town, is there a drop in rate? </h5>
<p>A one-day pass can be purchased for $10.</p>
 
<h5>Are there any times on the schedule where I can’t train?</h5>
<p>We have seasonal blackout times due to our gym being used for our professional athletes. However these only occur during the summer months and are typically only for a few hours in the late morning. We will provide sufficient notice of those dates on our facility calendar.</p>
 
