<h5>Are there discounts for couples?</h5>
<p>NLPT has a 10% discount for all family members that train with us. Please note that family members must be from the same household in order to receive the discount. It is only applicable to the Open Membership and NLPTfit Monthly Membership options of our adult fitness program.</p>
 
<h5>If I’m away, can I put my membership on hold?</h5>
<p>Yes, we are happy to freeze memberships. However when you resume training, we will start your new membership on the date that you return at full cost. So if your regular billing date is the 1st of each month and you return on the 25th of the same month, you will be charged full price on the 25th from that point forward.</p>
 
